#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:2
msgid "Workflow Patterns"
msgstr "工作流模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:4
msgid ""
"This guide documents common workflow patterns and best practices for "
"building Fabricatio applications."
msgstr ""
"本指南记录了构建 Fabricatio 应用程序时常见的工作流模式和最佳实践。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:7
msgid "Event Flow Overview"
msgstr "事件流概览"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:9
msgid "Fabricatio's event-driven architecture follows a consistent flow pattern:"
msgstr "Fabricatio 的事件驱动架构遵循一致的流程模式："

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:53
msgid "Simple Action Workflow"
msgstr "简单动作工作流"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:55
msgid "The most basic pattern - a single action responding to an event."
msgstr "最基本的模式——单个动作响应一个事件。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:99
msgid "Multi-Step Pipeline"
msgstr "多步骤流水线"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:101
msgid "Chain multiple actions where each step's output feeds into the next."
msgstr "将多个动作串联，每个步骤的输出作为下一个步骤的输入。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:171
msgid "Parallel Actions"
msgstr "并行动作"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:173
msgid "Execute multiple independent actions concurrently."
msgstr "并发执行多个相互独立的动作。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:233
msgid "Conditional Branching"
msgstr "条件分支"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:235
msgid "Use different workflows based on task characteristics."
msgstr "根据任务特征使用不同的工作流。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:291
msgid "Task Proposal Pattern"
msgstr "任务提议模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:293
msgid "Let the LLM decompose a goal into multiple tasks."
msgstr "让 LLM 将一个目标分解为多个任务。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:355
msgid "Error Handling Pattern"
msgstr "错误处理模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:357
msgid "Graceful error handling with fallback actions."
msgstr "通过回退动作实现优雅的错误处理。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:423
msgid "RAG Workflow Pattern"
msgstr "RAG 工作流模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:425
msgid "Retrieval-augmented generation with document ingestion and query."
msgstr "通过文档摄入和查询实现检索增强生成。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:499
msgid "Structured Output Pattern"
msgstr "结构化输出模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:501
msgid "Use Pydantic models for reliable structured responses."
msgstr "使用 Pydantic 模型实现可靠的结构化响应。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:567
msgid "Review-Improvement Loop"
msgstr "审查改进循环"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:569
msgid "Iterative refinement through review cycles."
msgstr "通过审查循环进行迭代优化。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:647
msgid "Checkpoint Pattern"
msgstr "检查点模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:649
msgid "Save workflow state for recovery."
msgstr "保存工作流状态以便恢复。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:715
msgid "Team Collaboration Pattern"
msgstr "团队协作模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:717
msgid "Multiple agents working together."
msgstr "多个智能体协同工作。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:792
msgid "EventEmitter Wildcard Pattern"
msgstr "EventEmitter 通配符模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:794
msgid "Using wildcards for flexible event routing."
msgstr "使用通配符实现灵活的事件路由。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:879
msgid "Task Lifecycle Pattern"
msgstr "任务生命周期模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:881
msgid "Task states and transitions."
msgstr "任务的状态与转换。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:943
msgid "Role and Skill Registration Pattern"
msgstr "角色与技能注册模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:945
msgid "How roles register and handle skills."
msgstr "角色如何注册和处理技能。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1014
msgid "Capability Mixin Pattern"
msgstr "能力混入模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1016
msgid "Combining capabilities with actions."
msgstr "将能力与动作组合。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1078
msgid "Role Inheritance Pattern"
msgstr "角色继承模式"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1080
msgid "Creating specialized roles through inheritance."
msgstr "通过继承创建专门化的角色。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1169
msgid "Best Practices Summary"
msgstr "最佳实践总结"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1171
msgid ""
"**Keep Actions Single-Purpose** Small, focused actions are easier to test"
" and reuse."
msgstr ""
"**保持动作单一职责** 小而专注的动作更易于测试和复用。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1174
msgid ""
"**Use Structured Output** ``aask_structured()`` provides reliable, typed "
"responses."
msgstr ""
"**使用结构化输出** ``aask_structured()`` 提供可靠、类型化的响应。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1177
msgid "**Handle Errors Explicitly** Use try/except and fallback workflows."
msgstr "**显式处理错误** 使用 try/except 和回退工作流。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1180
msgid "**Log Appropriately** Use ``logger`` for debugging and monitoring."
msgstr "**合理记录日志** 使用 ``logger`` 进行调试和监控。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1183
msgid "**Profile in Development** Use ``viztracer`` to identify bottlenecks."
msgstr "**在开发中进行性能分析** 使用 ``viztracer`` 识别性能瓶颈。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1186
msgid "**Configure Timeouts** Set reasonable timeouts for LLM calls."
msgstr "**配置超时** 为 LLM 调用设置合理的超时时间。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1189
msgid ""
"**Test Workflows Independently** Unit test actions, integration test "
"workflows."
msgstr ""
"**独立测试工作流** 对动作进行单元测试，对工作流进行集成测试。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1192
msgid ""
"**Use EventEmitter Wildcards Wisely** Wildcard patterns like ``user::*`` "
"enable flexible routing but avoid overly broad matches that could cause "
"unexpected behavior."
msgstr ""
"**明智地使用 EventEmitter 通配符** 像 ``user::*`` 这样的通配符模式可以实现灵活的路由，但应避免过于宽泛的匹配，以免导致意外行为。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1196
msgid ""
"**Leverage Capability Mixins** Combine capabilities to create powerful "
"actions without code duplication."
msgstr ""
"**善用能力混入** 组合能力以创建强大的动作，同时避免代码重复。"

#: ../../source/workflow-patterns.rst:1199
msgid ""
"**Design for Concurrency** Use ``asyncio.gather()`` for parallel action "
"execution when actions are independent."
msgstr ""
"**面向并发设计** 当动作相互独立时，使用 ``asyncio.gather()`` 进行并行动作执行。"
